<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 16:07:28 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列国防军公布在加沙 Al-Shifa 医院战斗中丧生的以色列士兵姓名</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-24/ty-article/idf-names-israeli-soldier-killed-in-combat-at-gazas-al-shifa-hospital/0000018e-70fb-d1c9-af8f-7efbc8270000</link><description>上士利奥尔·拉维夫周六在加沙北部的希法医院附近被杀，他的父母和三个兄弟姐妹幸存下来。战友们形容他是一位优秀、有道德、谦虚的军人</description><pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 15:19:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-24/ty-article/idf-names-israeli-soldier-killed-in-combat-at-gazas-al-shifa-hospital/0000018e-70fb-d1c9-af8f-7efbc8270000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防部长表示，他不会支持内塔尼亚胡豁免正统派的提案草案</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-24/ty-article/.premium/israeli-dm-says-wont-support-netanyahus-draft-proposal-that-exempts-haredim/0000018e-706a-ddf4-a3de-78fa0d140000</link><description>国防部长约阿夫·加兰特表示，他不能支持该大纲，这是对高等法院要求政府解释为何没有征召极端正统以色列人的禁令的回应，因为它没有得到整个联军和战时内阁的支持</description><pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 14:35:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-24/ty-article/.premium/israeli-dm-says-wont-support-netanyahus-draft-proposal-that-exempts-haredim/0000018e-706a-ddf4-a3de-78fa0d140000</guid></item><item><title>吐槽问题：以色列公司开发出第一个基于唾液的妊娠测试</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-24/ty-article/.premium/spit-at-the-question-israeli-company-develops-first-saliva-based-pregnancy-test/0000018e-701a-d1c9-af8f-7ebbb5b30000</link><description>这种名为 Salistick 的家庭测试可以在月经推迟的第一天就检测出 β-hCG 激素，而月经推迟十天后，这是大多数家庭尿液检测的标准，并且 96准确率百分比</description><pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 12:35:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-24/ty-article/.premium/spit-at-the-question-israeli-company-develops-first-saliva-based-pregnancy-test/0000018e-701a-d1c9-af8f-7ebbb5b30000</guid></item><item><title>犹太人为什么要盛装庆祝普珥节？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-24/ty-article/.premium/why-do-jews-dress-up-for-purim/0000017f-f77a-d044-adff-f7fb75f00000</link><description>借来的东西，借的东西？这一习俗似乎起源于 13 世纪的意大利，庆祝活动和化装舞会在忏悔星期二期间不断升级</description><pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 12:27:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-24/ty-article/.premium/why-do-jews-dress-up-for-purim/0000017f-f77a-d044-adff-f7fb75f00000</guid></item><item><title>“印度炸药”：在加沙，以色列国防军使用了 70 年前用于训练的弹药和炮弹</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-03-24/ty-article/a-huge-mess-in-gaza-idf-used-70-year-old-munitions-and-shells-intended-for-training/0000018e-5db4-d4b2-afcf-dfb626a90000</link><description>试图将弹药、非正规货物和“印度炸药”保存在分解的麻袋中，造成了后勤和行动上的噩梦，使炮兵部队难以协助作战部队，并增加了出错和错过目标的风险</description><pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 12:22:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-03-24/ty-article/a-huge-mess-in-gaza-idf-used-70-year-old-munitions-and-shells-intended-for-training/0000018e-5db4-d4b2-afcf-dfb626a90000</guid></item><item><title>战争结束五个月后，约旦河西岸和加沙地带的居民为哈马斯的袭击辩护</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-24/ty-article/.premium/five-months-into-the-war-residents-of-both-the-west-bank-and-gaza-justify-hamas-attack/0000018e-65ac-da37-a3ff-77bc473e0000</link><description>巴勒斯坦民意调查显示，加沙人对袭击的支持率从三个月前的 57% 大幅上升至 71%</description><pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 10:55:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-24/ty-article/.premium/five-months-into-the-war-residents-of-both-the-west-bank-and-gaza-justify-hamas-attack/0000018e-65ac-da37-a3ff-77bc473e0000</guid></item><item><title>托马斯·弗里德曼：“内塔尼亚胡将作为犹太历史上最糟糕的领导人被铭记”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-03-24/ty-article-podcast/thomas-friedman-netanyahu-is-the-worst-leader-in-jewish-history/0000018e-6d2f-d8e8-a9de-7dbfc2760000</link><description></description><pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 09:58:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-03-24/ty-article-podcast/thomas-friedman-netanyahu-is-the-worst-leader-in-jewish-history/0000018e-6d2f-d8e8-a9de-7dbfc2760000</guid></item><item><title>10 月 7 日哈马斯袭击导致以色列人权组织 B&amp;#39;Tselem 分裂</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-24/ty-article-magazine/.premium/to-be-a-leftist-in-israel-after-october-7-the-case-of-human-rights-group-btselem/0000018e-6f9c-df85-afde-ffdd3fc10000</link><description>10 月 7 日的大屠杀在以色列人权组织 B&amp;#39;Tselem 中造成了裂痕。一名前高管对其提起的诉讼，让我们难得一睹以色列左翼人士在解释对以色列的袭击事件时的争论。</description><pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 09:32:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-24/ty-article-magazine/.premium/to-be-a-leftist-in-israel-after-october-7-the-case-of-human-rights-group-btselem/0000018e-6f9c-df85-afde-ffdd3fc10000</guid></item><item><title>特拉维夫机场的廉价航站楼将于逾越节假期后重新开放</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-24/ty-article/.premium/tel-aviv-airports-budget-terminal-set-to-reopen-after-passover-holiday/0000018e-6f8a-d8e8-a9de-7fbb61890000</link><description>尽管低成本航空公司施压，要求尽快重新开放本古里安机场 1 号航站楼以适应逾越节旅行，但交通部表示，该机场将在 6 月 1 日之前恢复运营</description><pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 09:24:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-24/ty-article/.premium/tel-aviv-airports-budget-terminal-set-to-reopen-after-passover-holiday/0000018e-6f8a-d8e8-a9de-7fbb61890000</guid></item><item><title>辛贝特警告在美以色列人不要分享总理儿子的位置</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-03-24/ty-article/.premium/shin-bet-warns-israeli-in-u-s-not-to-share-location-of-pms-son/0000018e-6d06-d1c9-af8f-6faf4d390000</link><description>居住在国外的反对司法改革的抗议领袖奥菲尔·古特尔松(Offir Gutelzon)将他收到的警告描述为“令人不安的恐吓行为，侵犯了言论自由和抗议权利，这应该为我们所有人敲响警钟”</description><pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 04:16:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-03-24/ty-article/.premium/shin-bet-warns-israeli-in-u-s-not-to-share-location-of-pms-son/0000018e-6d06-d1c9-af8f-6faf4d390000</guid></item><item><title>美国正在改变对以色列的态度，以色列继续无视其警告</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-24/ty-article/.premium/the-u-s-is-changing-its-approach-with-israel-which-continues-to-ignore-its-warnings/0000018e-6d1b-dfa8-a98e-6f1b2db70000</link><description>美国表示强烈反对入侵拉法，因为没有看到保障在那里避难的巴勒斯坦人安全的计划。与此同时，以色列国防军在希法医院的行动中取得了重大进展，以色列希望该医院能够成为对抗哈马斯的筹码</description><pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 04:10:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-24/ty-article/.premium/the-u-s-is-changing-its-approach-with-israel-which-continues-to-ignore-its-warnings/0000018e-6d1b-dfa8-a98e-6f1b2db70000</guid></item><item><title>“巨大错误”：如果以色列入侵拉法，卡马拉·哈里斯“不排除任何可能性”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-24/ty-article-live/idf-about-fifty-launches-from-lebanon-detected-air-force-attacks-in-lebanon-syria/0000018e-6e59-d8e8-a9de-7efbfff50000</link><description>巴勒斯坦红新月会：以色列国防军正在围困加沙的纳赛尔医院和阿迈勒医院 ■ 黎巴嫩的报道：无人机袭击了该国东部苏埃里的车辆 ■ 以色列国防军和辛贝特部队从连夜开始对汗尤尼斯采取行动 ■ 上士利奥尔·拉维夫， 21 岁，在 Al-Shifa 医院附近的战斗中身亡 ■ 以色列袭击黎巴嫩真主党目标，周日晚间向以色列北部发射了大约 50 枚火箭 ■ 美国正式禁止向近东救济工程处提供资助直至 2025 年 3 月</description><pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 04:03:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-24/ty-article-live/idf-about-fifty-launches-from-lebanon-detected-air-force-attacks-in-lebanon-syria/0000018e-6e59-d8e8-a9de-7efbfff50000</guid></item><item><title>回顾普珥节的故事，数千人在特拉维夫集会要求释放人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-23/ty-article/.premium/recalling-the-story-of-purim-thousands-rally-in-tel-aviv-for-the-release-of-the-hostages/0000018e-6ca0-d8e8-a9de-7cbbe4b10000</link><description>“这样的事情是不可接受的，在我们的犹太教中是不可接受的”：在讲述哈曼试图消灭犹太人的普珥节故事时，仍被扣押在加沙的人质家属恳求全国团结起来，将他们全部带回家</description><pubDate>Sat, 23 Mar 2024 21:00:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-23/ty-article/.premium/recalling-the-story-of-purim-thousands-rally-in-tel-aviv-for-the-release-of-the-hostages/0000018e-6ca0-d8e8-a9de-7cbbe4b10000</guid></item><item><title>托尼·库什纳：“自加沙战争以来，我更加认识到抵制以色列是必要的。但我做不到&amp;#39;</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2024-03-23/ty-article-magazine/.premium/since-the-gaza-war-i-moved-closer-to-the-idea-of-boycotting-israel-but-i-cant-do-it/0000018e-6a82-dfa8-a98e-6f8b31590000</link><description>剧作家托尼·库什纳告诉《国土报》播客，他支持乔纳森·格雷泽在加沙演讲中的每一个字，解释了为什么犹太复国主义不等于种族主义，并坚称“左派中有一部分人很天真，比反犹太主义还要天真”。阅读完整采访</description><pubDate>Sat, 23 Mar 2024 20:28:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2024-03-23/ty-article-magazine/.premium/since-the-gaza-war-i-moved-closer-to-the-idea-of-boycotting-israel-but-i-cant-do-it/0000018e-6a82-dfa8-a98e-6f8b31590000</guid></item><item><title>“总理，你很困惑：公众希望所有人质回家”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-23/ty-article/.premium/prime-minister-you-are-confused-the-public-wants-all-the-hostages-home/0000018e-6caf-d16d-a58e-7cafe5a80000</link><description>以色列各地数千人抗议内塔尼亚胡政府和人质协议。在特拉维夫，数百名抗议者纵火并封锁主要道路。仍被扣押在加沙的一名人质的母亲在多哈向以色列代表团发表讲话：“你们正在履行自己一生的使命——没有人质协议就不要回来”</description><pubDate>Sat, 23 Mar 2024 20:03:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-23/ty-article/.premium/prime-minister-you-are-confused-the-public-wants-all-the-hostages-home/0000018e-6caf-d16d-a58e-7cafe5a80000</guid></item><item><title>官员称以色列同意美国人质交易提议，哈马斯尚未回应</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-23/ty-article/.premium/israel-agrees-to-u-s-hostage-deal-proposal-hamas-yet-to-respond-official-says/0000018e-6cb4-d16d-a58e-7cb5daab0000</link><description>据该官员称，该提案涉及释放协议中的首批 40 名人质。哈马斯领导层的消息人士告诉《国土报》，以色列官员的言论是“以色列的操纵行为，为继续战争辩护”</description><pubDate>Sat, 23 Mar 2024 19:40:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-23/ty-article/.premium/israel-agrees-to-u-s-hostage-deal-proposal-hamas-yet-to-respond-official-says/0000018e-6cb4-d16d-a58e-7cb5daab0000</guid></item><item><title>你需要知道的，第 169 天：联合国秘书长视察拉法过境点，美国正式禁止向近东救济工程处提供资金</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-23/ty-article/.premium/what-you-need-to-know-day-169-un-chief-visits-rafah-crossing-u-s-blocks-unrwa-funding/0000018e-6c61-d477-abbf-ef617edb0000</link><description>联合国秘书长视察拉法过境点，谴责封锁那里的援助卡车是“道德义愤” ■ 美国正式禁止向近东救济工程处提供资金直至 2025 年 3 月 ■ 以色列国防军表示，在 Al-Shifa 医院拘留了至少 800 名嫌疑人，并杀死了 170 名哈马斯成员 ■ 白宫分享拉法向以色列官员发起进攻的其他选择 ■ 战争结束 169 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Sat, 23 Mar 2024 18:20:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-23/ty-article/.premium/what-you-need-to-know-day-169-un-chief-visits-rafah-crossing-u-s-blocks-unrwa-funding/0000018e-6c61-d477-abbf-ef617edb0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列士兵在周五约旦河西岸枪击事件中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-23/ty-article/israeli-soldier-killed-in-fridays-west-bank-shooting-attack/0000018e-6c60-d1c9-af8f-6ee9ad390000</link><description>中士。伊莱·大卫·加芬克尔 (Ilay David Garfinkel) 中士在以色列国防军杜夫德万部队服役，在士兵们在茂密植被的地区追击时被袭击者杀害。另外七名士兵在袭击中受伤</description><pubDate>Sat, 23 Mar 2024 18:18:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-23/ty-article/israeli-soldier-killed-in-fridays-west-bank-shooting-attack/0000018e-6c60-d1c9-af8f-6ee9ad390000</guid></item><item><title>犹太节日万圣节普珥节简史</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-23/ty-article-magazine/the-odd-history-of-purim-the-halloween-of-jewish-holidays/00000180-5bae-df19-a7f3-dbfe31760000</link><description>它的起源是什么？什么时候开始的？为什么许多犹太人蔑视普珥节——背后的爱情、谋杀和背叛故事是真的吗？</description><pubDate>Sat, 23 Mar 2024 17:04:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-23/ty-article-magazine/the-odd-history-of-purim-the-halloween-of-jewish-holidays/00000180-5bae-df19-a7f3-dbfe31760000</guid></item><item><title>民主党警告拜登：以色列作为军事援助接受国不遵守美国法律</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-23/ty-article/.premium/democrats-warn-biden-israel-not-in-compliance-with-u-s-law-as-recipients-of-military-aid/0000018e-6bcb-d8e8-a9de-7ffbe23f0000</link><description>民主党议员警告美国总统，内塔尼亚胡政府对向加沙运送人道主义援助的限制使以色列“没有资格继续获得美国武器”，必须纠正这种情况，以免开创“不可接受的先例”</description><pubDate>Sat, 23 Mar 2024 16:00:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-23/ty-article/.premium/democrats-warn-biden-israel-not-in-compliance-with-u-s-law-as-recipients-of-military-aid/0000018e-6bcb-d8e8-a9de-7ffbe23f0000</guid></item></channel></rss>